About Us
Whisperwood is a 55+ community that caters to the needs of a wide variety of people looking to live a comfortable adult lifestyle. The beautifully decorated clubhouse has a British West Indies theme and provides a landscaped resort atmosphere to enjoy while you listen to soothing music and relax in the sun. If the sun isn’t your cup of tea you can grab a book from the library, kick back, take your shoes off and sit under the covered patio by our 2 swimming pools.
Billiard table
Poker tables
Lighted tennis and pickle ball court
Lighted shuffleboard courts
9-hole pitch & putt golf course
Large banquet room with solid red oak dance floor
Library
Swimming pools
Bocce ball courts
Pickle Ball
Beautiful decorated clubhouse
Fully equipped commercial kitchen for resident's use
Besides the amenities at Whisperwood we also have a wide selection of groups and clubs you can join to expand your friendships and fun. Check out our activity calendar.
